        public static Parameters valueOf(Map<String,Object> value)
        Creates a Parameters instance representing the specified Map<String, Item> value.

        Note that the Map implementation that is used here needs to iterate predictably based on insertion order, such as LinkedHashMap.

        Parameters:
        value - a Map<String, Item> value
        Returns:
        a Parameters representing value.
